26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_pmu_gf100.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:35 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "priv.h"
30#include "fuc/gf100.fuc3.h"
31
32static const struct nvkm_pmu_func
33gf100_pmu = {
34 .code.data = gf100_pmu_code,
35 .code.size = sizeof(gf100_pmu_code),
36 .data.data = gf100_pmu_data,
37 .data.size = sizeof(gf100_pmu_data),
38};
39
40int
41gf100_pmu_new(struct nvkm_device *device, int index, struct nvkm_pmu **ppmu)
42{
43 return nvkm_pmu_new_(&gf100_pmu, device, index, ppmu);
44}
